    <small>证据覆盖：已就绪 ${escapeHtml(String(process.evidenceCoverage.readySourceCount))} 类，缺失 ${escapeHtml(String(process.evidenceCoverage.missingSourceCount))} 类${missingSources}。${escapeHtml(process.disclaimer)}</small>
